    "course_title": "BI/PAN/ASEXUALITY: COMMUNITY & REPRESENTATION",
    "description": "Explore the experiences, needs, and goals of bisexual/biromantic, pansexual/panromantic, and asexual/aromantic (BPA) people, as well as their interactions with the mainstream lesbian  gay community. Consider outcome disparities, community coalition building, and media representation. Explore how multiple marginalization within BPA communities may complicate analysis of members' experiences.",
